      "rationale": "A two-level mesh refinement study was performed (coarse and medium only). Extrapolation to the fine-mesh limit was not completed due to computational resource constraints. The reported GCI of 8.3% for the normalized hemolysis index exceeds the 5% threshold, and the asymptotic convergence range has not been confirmed. No corrective action was taken prior to finalising the assessment."
